00:19:11,669 --> 00:19:18,433
This approach won't necessarily work for everything, but for us, defining a distinct set of rules for color usage,

312
00:19:19,133 --> 00:19:24,976
our team simplified the production process, reduced arguments, and made all our choices easier.

